# Nobel Prize Winners Web App

This web app allows you to explore Nobel Prize laureates and specifically highlights laureates who have won the prize more than once.

## Features

- Display Nobel Prize laureates by year and category.
- Automatically show information about laureates who have won more than once.
- Filter laureates by year (select a year from the dropdown).

## How to Use

1. Clone this repository to your local machine.

2. Open `index.html` in your web browser to run the app.

3. Select a year from the dropdown to see Nobel Prize winners for that year.

4. The app will automatically display information about laureates who have won the prize more than once.

## Data Source

The data is fetched from a JSON file (`data.json`) that contains information about Nobel Prize laureates.

## Development

This project uses HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. You can modify the code to customize the app as needed.

